name: Lily Part 02
description:
Another visualizer of DUARA's song called 'Lily Part 1,2'.
Consist of 3 main elements: DUARA that means 'praying' in Turkish, Lily as symbol of 'purity', also wolf that knows as 'great-spirit' in japanese.
1920x1080. 20s motiongraphic.
Audio also made by myself due to copyright issue.
